The prep pipeline already has a hook for exactly this experiment: keep one extra generated clarification variant per near-duplicate family. Itâ€™s currently disabled. Enabling that selectively is a narrow change, and it should raise coverage on prompts like â€œWhat should I do next?â€ and â€œWould this work?â€ without changing optimization or benchmark parsing.
